pan> who I thought wasn't going to be able to enter the contest, so whatever. I already dedicated it to you, and I'm not undedicating it.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Attribution</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Extraordinarily&nbsp;Mundane</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><a href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/68/RJC1_PJC.jpg/1280px-RJC1_PJC.jpg" target="_blank">Image</a></p> </div> </div> </div> 
